name: BAGELS
description:
Bagels is a miscellaneous game, developed and published by Compute! Publications, which was released in 1992. This is a version written in JavaScript by Neo-OmegaSoft.
Extracted from classicbasicgames.org

You can play in the  Official BAGELS Gamepage
